works.description:
Metalum Limited (Gambia) are specialist suppliers of different types of floor and roofing sheets and tiles which includes (Decrabond) Decra® Roof Systems.

These tiles which have good durability due to the combination of galvanised steel and granular stone coating. Such roofs have rugged all weather resistance to salt water which makes them ideal for houses built near the Atlantic Ocean.

The company also offer low maintenance and quick installation because it uses a minimum number of fasteners due to its interlocking design. This system was introduced in Ireland and the UK in 1977 which means that it is made to the European Standard.

Through its retail outlet in Kanifing the company also has for sale sanitary ware, kitchens, ceramic, porcelain and swimming pool tiles.
